T02D3189:201a-1: sngar bshad pa'i cho gas stong pa nyid bsgoms pa'i rjes la /
T02D3189:201a-2: padma'i zla ba'i dkyil 'khor gyi steng du thig le dkar po rnam par bsgom par bya ste /
T02D3189:201a-3: spro bar bya ba la sogs pa sngon du btang
T02D3189:201a-4: zhing de yongs su gyur pa las yi ge dh'i:
T02D3189:201a-5: dkar pos bskyed pa'i 'jam dpal aa ra pa tsa
T02D3189:201a-6: na dkar po gcig pu nyid 'ba' zhig go //
T02D3189:201a-7: rang nyid kyi sa bon snying gar rnam par bsams la /
T02D3189:201a-10: rig pa 'dzin pa'i sde snod nas 'byung ba'i 'jam dpal gyi sgrub thabs mdor bstan pa'o //
